# TypeScript & Next.js

- Use TypeScript strict mode (already configured)
- Prefer type-safe patterns and avoid `any` types
- Use Next.js 16 App Router conventions
- Components should be React Server Components by default unless client-side interactivity is needed
- Use the `"use client"` directive only when necessary
- Use ESLint for code quality checks
